title: Android 4.3 has some really bad issues with the `crypto` package, that even whenâ€¦
message:
Android 4.3 has some really bad issues with the `crypto` package, that even when fixed mean there's some results that are backward incompatible with the versions that operate okay.

This commit will force all Android 4.3 users to the error page, a futher commit (after deploying) this will bump the android minSdkVersion so that this version is the last they will get.
